#

Classic Split Pea Soup

135 min
$12.5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Fiber

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A hearty and comforting split pea soup, perfect for any season, rich in flavor and nutrients.

Ingredients

  • split peas: 2 cups
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • bay leaf: 1
  • black pepper: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
